{
  "_INSTRUCTIONS": [
    "This is a placeholder. To enable Firebase push notifications:",
    "1. Create a Firebase project at https://console.firebase.google.com",
    "2. Add an Android app with package name: com.paprika.paprika_merchant",
    "3. Download google-services.json from the Firebase console",
    "4. Place it at: android/app/google-services.json",
    "5. Add the google-services Gradle plugin to android/app/build.gradle.kts:",
    "     plugins { id(\"com.google.gms.google-services\") }",
    "   and in android/settings.gradle.kts plugins block:",
    "     id(\"com.google.gms.google-services\") version \"4.4.2\" apply false",
    "6. Run WITHOUT --dart-define=ENABLE_FIREBASE=false (or set it to true)",
    "",
    "For simulator-only development, skip this file entirely and use:",
    "  flutter run --dart-define=ENABLE_FIREBASE=false ..."
  ],
